 director of sport Vanessa Turner told the Standard: \\\"The whole school has been watching it's just phenomenal, we are just so proud.\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 1011, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 898, \"end\": 905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vanessa_Redgrave\", \"score\": 0.9647304054994182, \"rank\": 0.03655901403690039, \"text\": \"Vanessa\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vanessa_Redgrave\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vanessa_Redgrave\"}, {\"begin\": 906, \"end\": 912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Broadcasting_System\", \"score\": 0.989859095223769, \"rank\": 0.00893221697513107, \"text\": \"Turner\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Broadcasting_System\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Broadcasting_System\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The school's director\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 888}, {\"ngram\": \"the Standard\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 930}, {\"ngram\": \"The whole school\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 949}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is a once in a lifetime.\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1043, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lifetime\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1042}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We feel very privileged to know Alex and to follow his career has been incredible.\\\"\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1127, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1076, \"end\": 1080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"score\": 0.999999998329713, \"rank\": 1.6702553587998378e-09, \"text\": \"Alex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1105}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reflecting on the race's dramatic finish, which saw Yee make up a 14-second gap on the leaderNew Zealand's Hayden White before making a huge break for gold, she said: \\\"A couple of seconds or a second is a big thing to make up.\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1355, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1236, \"end\": 1248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hayden_White\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2434021885891038e-15, \"text\": \"Hayden White\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hayden_White\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hayden_White\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race's dramatic finish\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1169}, {\"ngram\": \"Yee\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1184}, {\"ngram\": \"a 14-second gap\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1208}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge break\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1275}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1284}, {\"ngram\": \"A couple\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1305}, {\"ngram\": \"seconds\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"a second\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1328}, {\"ngram\": \"a big thing\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1343}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To make up on that amount of distance and then to keep going and lead by that distance is just mindblowing.\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1465, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that amount\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1383}, {\"ngram\": \"distance\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1395}, {\"ngram\": \"that distance\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1444}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"(We felt) humbled to be able to witness something like that and realise we know such an amazing athlete.\\\"\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1573, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1517}, {\"ngram\": \"such an amazing athlete\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1571}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ms Turner recalled the moment she first met Yee when he was in primary school and signed up for a sports scholarship assessment.\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1578, \"end\": 1584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Broadcasting_System\", \"score\": 0.989859095223769, \"rank\": 0.00893221697513107, \"text\": \"Turner\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Broadcasting_System\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Broadcasting_System\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1604}, {\"ngram\": \"Yee\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1622}, {\"ngram\": \"primary school\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1652}, {\"ngram\": \"a sports scholarship assessment\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1702}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She explained that it was clear at that stage how talented he was when he outpaced a PE teacher during a bleep test.\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1821, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1790, \"end\": 1792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Physical_education\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.374004951885368e-14, \"text\": \"PE\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Physical_education\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Physical_education\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that stage\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1750}, {\"ngram\": \"a bleep test\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1820}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"We used to do it so that the staff would pace the children all the way through - until we met Alex.\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1928, \"end\": 1932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"score\": 0.999999998329713, \"rank\": 1.6702553587998378e-09, \"text\": \"Alex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the staff\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1868}, {\"ngram\": \"the children\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1892}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He just kept running and running and running and outpaced the member of staff running with him.\\\"\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 2032, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the member\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2004}, {\"ngram\": \"staff\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2013}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yee, now 26, \\\"put the school on the map\\\" competing in a range of athletics and cross-country competitions, as well as representing the school in badminton.\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2189, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yee\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2037}, {\"ngram\": \"the school\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2062}, {\"ngram\": \"the map\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2073}, {\"ngram\": \"a range\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2095}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 2099, \"to\": 2108}, {\"ngram\": \"cross-country competitions\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2139}, {\"ngram\": \"the school\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2175}, {\"ngram\": \"badminton\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2188}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stranger Things star says school mates 'do not care' that she was in the show London buses set for more disruption as drivers vote for strikes again Track athlete chases down London phone thief and retrieves mobile - watch Incredible days out and trips for autumn and winter Recalling his time at the school, between 2009 and 2017, Ms Turner added: \\\"Alex has always been and continues to be an amazing role model for other young athletes and students.\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2270, \"end\": 2282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buses_in_London\", \"score\": 0.9998715858213111, \"rank\": 0.00012843067117341198, \"text\": \"London buses\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buses_in_London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buses_in_London\"}, {\"begin\": 2368, \"end\": 2374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999998414941854, \"rank\": 1.5515881906619065e-07, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 2530, \"end\": 2536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Broadcasting_System\", \"score\": 0.989859095223769, \"rank\": 0.00893221697513107, \"text\": \"Turner\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Broadcasting_System\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Broadcasting_System\"}, {\"begin\": 2545, \"end\": 2549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"score\": 0.999999998329713, \"rank\": 1.6702553587998378e-09, \"text\": \"Alex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Stranger Things star\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2211}, {\"ngram\": \"school mates\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2229}, {\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2268}, {\"ngram\": \"more disruption\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2305}, {\"ngram\": \"drivers\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"strikes\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2333}, {\"ngram\": \"Track athlete chases\", \"from\": 2340, \"to\": 2360}, {\"ngram\": \"autumn\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2454}, {\"ngram\": \"winter\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2465}, {\"ngram\": \"his time\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2484}, {\"ngram\": \"the school\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2498}, {\"ngram\": \"Alex\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2545}, {\"ngram\": \"an amazing role model\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2603}, {\"ngram\": \"other young athletes\", \"from\": 2608, \"to\": 2628}, {\"ngram\": \"students\", \"from\": 2633, \"to\": 2641}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not believe he was ever naughty.\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2684, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was quiet, he was polite.\", \"from\": 2685, \"to\": 2713, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He is so calm, measured, in control of himself.\", \"from\": 2715, \"to\": 2763, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"control\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2751}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I never saw him get angry or anything like that.\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2814, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2795, \"to\": 2803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is just a really lovely guy and there is a really lovely family behind him who were really supportive and 100 per cent involved in everything he was doing.\\\"\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 2974, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just a really lovely guy\", \"from\": 2821, \"to\": 2845}, {\"ngram\": \"a really lovely family\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 2881}, {\"ngram\": \"really supportive and 100 per cent\", \"from\": 2902, \"to\": 2936}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2949, \"to\": 2959}]}, {\"sentence\": \"New posters will now be put up around the school to celebrate the Olympian's success and Yee's former classmates have been getting in touch to tell the school they are thrilled with the result.\", \"from\": 2976, \"to\": 3169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3042, \"end\": 3050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999692781789, \"rank\": 3.072141593847671e-08, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"New posters\", \"from\": 2976, \"to\": 2987}, {\"ngram\": \"the school\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3024}, {\"ngram\": \"Yee's former classmates\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3088}, {\"ngram\": \"touch\", \"from\": 3110, \"to\": 3115}, {\"ngram\": \"the school\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3134}, {\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 3158, \"to\": 3168}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Acting operational headteacher Andrew Sear told the Standard: \\\"What has been lovely is we have had lots of ex-students messaging the school talking about how proud they are to have known him.\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3362, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Acting operational headteacher Andrew Sear\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3213}, {\"ngram\": \"the Standard\", \"from\": 3219, \"to\": 3231}, {\"ngram\": \"lots\", \"from\": 3270, \"to\": 3274}, {\"ngram\": \"ex\", \"from\": 3278, \"to\": 3280}, {\"ngram\": \"students\", \"from\": 3281, \"to\": 3289}, {\"ngram\": \"the school\", \"from\": 3300, \"to\": 3310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone is extremely proud to have that association with him.\", \"from\": 3364, \"to\": 3427, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 3365, \"to\": 3373}, {\"ngram\": \"that association\", \"from\": 3401, \"to\": 3417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It inspires the next generation of sports scholars and non-scholars to succeed as they can see that they can do it with hard work and determination.\\\"\", \"from\": 3428, \"to\": 3577, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the next generation\", \"from\": 3440, \"to\": 3459}, {\"ngram\": \"sports scholars\", \"from\": 3463, \"to\": 3478}, {\"ngram\": \"non\", \"from\": 3483, \"to\": 3486}, {\"ngram\": \"scholars\", \"from\": 3487, \"to\": 3495}, {\"ngram\": \"hard work\", \"from\": 3548, \"to\": 3557}, {\"ngram\": \"determination\", \"from\": 3562, \"to\": 3575}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reflecting on what Yee was like at school he added: \\\"What you see with him is what you get.\", \"from\": 3579, \"to\": 3670, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yee\", \"from\": 3598, \"to\": 3601}, {\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 3614, \"to\": 3620}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is a lovely guy.\", \"from\": 3671, \"to\": 3690, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lovely guy\", \"from\": 3677, \"to\": 3689}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was a fantastic student, a really nice student and it looks like he has developed into a really lovely young man.\\\"\", \"from\": 3691, \"to\": 3808,